<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg"><link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json"><meta name="theme-color" content="#6366F1"><link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon.svg"><title>DormTool – Your Complete College Transition Toolkit</title><script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-C7V3YR4WTZ"></script><script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-C7V3YR4WTZ');</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"DormTool – Your Complete College Transition Toolkit","description":"Free interactive tools for college students: dorm checklist, laundry timer, move-out checklist, moving cost calculator, rent affordability calculator, bill splitter, and first apartment checklist.","url":"https://dormtool.com/","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"SettleList Labs","url":"https://dormtool.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://dormtool.com/"},"mentions":[{"@type":"WebPage","name":"DormTool Hub","url":"https://dormtool.com/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Dorm Checklist","url":"https://dormtool.com/dorm-checklist/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Dorm Laundry Hub","url":"https://dormtool.com/dorm-laundry-hub/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Move-Out Checklist","url":"https://dormtool.com/move-out-checklist/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Moving Cost Calculator","url":"https://dormtool.com/moving-cost-calculator/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"First Apartment Checklist","url":"https://dormtool.com/first-apartment-checklist/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Rent Affordability Calculator","url":"https://dormtool.com/rent-affordability/"},{"@type":"WebPage","name":"Roommate Bill Splitter","url":"https://dormtool.com/bill-splitter/"}]}</script><meta name="description" content="Free interactive tools for college students: dorm checklist, laundry timer, move-out checklist, moving cost calculator, rent affordability calculator, bill splitter, and first apartment checklist."><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"><style>*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}:root{--hub-primary:#0F172A;--hub-primary-light:#1E293B;--hub-accent:#6366F1;--hub-accent-hover:#4F46E5;--hub-cta:#F59E0B;--hub-cta-hover:#D97706;--hub-cta-text:#1F2937;--success:#10B981;--success-light:#D1FAE5;--success-dark:#065F46;--bg:#F8F9FA;--card:#FFF;--card-hover:#F1F5F9;--text:#1F2937;--text-light:#6B7280;--text-muted:#9CA3AF;--border:#E5E7EB;--border-light:#F1F3F5;--shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.06);--shadow-lg:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.1);--radius:12px;--radius-sm:8px;--radius-xl:16px;--font:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--max-w:1200px}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{font-family:var(--font);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}::selection{background:var(--hub-accent);color:#fff}img{max-width:100%;display:block}.hub-header{background:var(--hub-primary);color:#fff;padding:20px 20px 16px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}.hub-header .hub-inner{max-width:var(--max-w);margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px}.hub-logo{font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;letter-spacing:-.5px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:#fff}.hub-logo span{color:var(--hub-accent)}.hub-tagline{font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);display:none}@media(min-width:640px){.hub-tagline{display:block}}.hub-badge{font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;background:var(--hub-accent);color:#fff;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.3px;text-transform:uppercase}.hub-header-sub{max-width:var(--max-w);margin:6px auto 0;font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);text-align:center;padding:0 20px}@media(min-width:640px){.hub-header-sub{text-align:right;padding:0}}.hub-container{max-width:var(--max-w);margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 40px;flex:1;width:100%}.hub-cat-nav{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}.hub-cat-btn{padding:10px 22px;border:none;border-radius:24px;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;background:var(--card);color:var(--text-light);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:var(--shadow);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border:2px solid transparent}.hub-cat-btn:hover{color:var(--hub-accent);border-color:var(--border);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}.hub-cat-btn.is-active{background:var(--hub-accent);color:#fff;border-color:var(--hub-accent);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(99,102,241,.3)}.hub-cat-btn .cat-count{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:500;opacity:.6;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);padding:1px 8px;border-radius:10px;margin-left:2px}.hub-cat-btn.is-active .cat-count{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);opacity:.9}.hub-cat-btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--hub-cta);outline-offset:2px}.hub-cards{display:none;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}.hub-cards.is-visible{display:grid}@media(min-width:540px){.hub-cards{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}.hub-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);border:1px solid var(--border);transition:all .25s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.hub-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--hub-accent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .25s}.hub-card:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);border-color:var(--hub-accent);transform:translateY(-2px)}.hub-card:hover::before{opacity:1}.hub-card .hc-emoji{font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1}.hub-card .hc-title{font-size:1.02rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3}.hub-card .hc-highlight{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.5;flex:1;margin-bottom:14px}.hub-card .hc-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center}.hub-card .hc-btn{padding:9px 18px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-family:var(--font);font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;line-height:1.2}.hc-btn-launch{background:var(--hub-cta);color:var(--hub-cta-text);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(245,158,11,.25)}.hc-btn-launch:hover{background:var(--hub-cta-hover);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(245,158,11,.35)}.hc-btn-launch:active{transform:translateY(0)}.hc-btn-preview{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light);border:1px solid var(--border)}.hc-btn-preview:hover{background:var(--card-hover);color:var(--text)}.hc-btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--hub-accent);outline-offset:2px}.hub-intro{text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px}.hub-intro h1{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--hub-primary);letter-spacing:-.5px}.hub-intro h1 span{color:var(--hub-accent)}.hub-intro p{color:var(--text-light);font-size:.9rem;margin-top:6px;max-width:620px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}.hub-ad{background:var(--card);border:2px dashed var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);text-align:center;padding:18px;margin:14px 0;color:var(--text-light);font-size:.78rem;min-height:90px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:border-color .2s}.hub-ad:hover{border-color:var(--hub-accent)}.hub-ad--tall{min-height:160px}.hub-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:20px 0 16px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}.hub-divider::before,.hub-divider::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app{--primary:#1A237E;--primary-light:#3949AB;--primary-dark:#0D1642;--accent:#FF6B35;--accent-hover:#E55A2B;--success:#10B981;--success-light:#D1FAE5;--bg:#F4F5F7;--card:#FFF;--text:#1F2937;--text-light:#6B7280;--border:#E5E7EB;--shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.06);--radius:12px;--radius-sm:8px;--font:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--max-w:1200px;margin-top:8px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-header{background:var(--primary);color:#fff;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-header .dc-title{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-header .dc-title span{color:var(--accent)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-header .dc-sub{font-size:.72rem;opacity:.7}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-body{background:var(--card);border-radius:0 0 var(--radius) var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:16px 18px 18px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress{background:var(--bg);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress .dc-pstats{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;color:var(--text)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress .dc-pstats span{color:var(--primary)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress .dc-pbar{flex:1;min-width:80px;height:8px;background:var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress .dc-pfill{height:100%;width:0%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-light));border-radius:6px;transition:width .45s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress .dc-plabel{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-light);min-width:32px;text-align:right;font-weight:600}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress.is-done .dc-pfill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--success),#34D399)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress.is-done .dc-plabel{color:var(--success)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-budget{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-light);padding:0 14px 8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-budget strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:700}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-budget .dc-bnote{font-size:.64rem;color:var(--text-muted)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-wrap{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0 0;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04);margin:0;padding:8px 10px 0;position:relative;border:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:none}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-scroll{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;overflow:visible;padding-bottom:4px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-wrap:hover .dc-tabs-scroll{scrollbar-color:var(--border) transparent}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar{height:3px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:transparent;border-radius:4px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tabs-wrap:hover .dc-tabs-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tab-btn{flex-shrink:0;padding:6px 14px;border:none;border-radius:16px;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.76rem;font-weight:600;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light);cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .18s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tab-btn:hover{background:#E8EAF6;color:var(--primary)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tab-btn.is-active{background:var(--primary);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(26,35,126,.25)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tab-btn .dc-tcount{font-size:.64rem;font-weight:500;opacity:.6;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:8px;margin-left:2px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-tab-btn.is-active .dc-tcount{opacity:.9;background:rgba(255,255,255,.18)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-panel{padding:12px 14px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm);background:var(--card)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-pheader{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--bg);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ptitle{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-catactions{display:flex;gap:4px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-catactions button{padding:3px 10px;border:none;border-radius:10px;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-selall{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-selall:hover{background:#E8EAF6;color:var(--primary)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-desel{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-desel:hover{background:#FEE2E2;color:#DC2626}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:6px}@media(min-width:640px){#dorm-checklist-app .dc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-layout{overflow-x:hidden;max-width:100%}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-body{overflow-x:hidden}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-panel{overflow-x:hidden}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-width:0;background:var(--bg);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:8px 10px;transition:all .18s;border:2px solid transparent}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item:hover{border-color:var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked{background:var(--success-light);border-color:var(--success)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked .dc-iname{font-weight:600}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-irow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;min-width:0}@media(min-width:640px){#dorm-checklist-app .dc-irow{flex-wrap:nowrap;gap:7px}}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ichk{cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;flex:1;min-width:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ichk input{position:absolute;opacity:0;width:0;height:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ibox{flex-shrink:0;width:17px;height:17px;border:2px solid #CBD5E1;border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .2s;background:var(--card)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ichk input:checked~.dc-ibox{background:var(--success);border-color:var(--success)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ibox svg{opacity:0;transition:opacity .12s;width:9px;height:9px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ichk input:checked~.dc-ibox svg{opacity:1}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-iemoji{font-size:.95rem;flex-shrink:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-iname{font-size:.8rem;font-weight:500;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-idesc{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:1px;margin-left:50px;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:1;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop{font-size:.66rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;background:var(--accent);padding:3px 9px;border-radius:4px;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1.3}@media(max-width:420px){#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop{font-size:.6rem;padding:2px 6px}}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop:hover{background:var(--accent-hover);transform:translateY(-1px)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop:active{transform:translateY(0)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop.is-incart{background:var(--success)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ishop.is-incart:hover{background:#059669}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item--custom{background:#FFF8E1;border-color:#FFE082}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item--custom.is-checked{background:var(--success-light);border-color:var(--success)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item--custom .dc-iemoji{font-size:.75rem;opacity:.6}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item--custom .dc-iname::after{content:'Custom';font-size:.58rem;color:var(--text-light);background:var(--border);padding:0 5px;border-radius:3px;margin-left:4px;font-weight:400}.dc-main{min-width:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-iremove{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-light);padding:2px 4px;border-radius:3px;transition:all .12s;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-iremove:hover{color:#DC2626;background:#FEE2E2}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-addform{grid-column:1/-1;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:3px;padding-top:6px;border-top:1px dashed var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-addinput{flex:1;padding:7px 9px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-family:var(--font);font-size:.78rem;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;background:var(--card)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-addinput:focus{border-color:var(--primary)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-addbtn{padding:7px 12px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--primary);color:#fff;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.76rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s;white-space:nowrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-addbtn:hover{background:var(--primary-dark)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-bottombar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:12px;padding-top:10px;border-top:2px solid var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btsummary{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-light);font-weight:500}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btactions{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btactions button,#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btactions a{padding:7px 14px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-family:var(--font);font-size:.76rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-print{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-print:hover{background:var(--primary-dark)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-reset{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light);border:1px solid var(--border)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-btn-reset:hover{background:#FEE2E2;color:#DC2626;border-color:#FECACA}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-sidebar{display:none}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-layout{display:block;gap:14px}@media(min-width:1024px){#dorm-checklist-app .dc-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-sidebar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);border:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:76px;max-height:calc(100vh - 90px);overflow:hidden}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cheader{padding:12px 14px 8px;font-size:.88rem;font-weight:700;border-bottom:2px solid var(--bg);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-citems{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:6px 10px;min-height:50px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cempty{text-align:center;color:var(--text-light);font-size:.76rem;padding:24px 8px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 5px;border-radius:5px;transition:background .12s}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item:hover{background:var(--bg)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item .ci-emoji{font-size:.85rem;flex-shrink:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item .ci-name{font-size:.76rem;flex:1;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item .ci-remove{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-light);padding:2px 4px;border-radius:3px;transition:all .1s;flex-shrink:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cart-item .ci-remove:hover{color:#DC2626;background:#FEE2E2}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-cfooter{padding:8px 12px 12px;border-top:2px solid var(--bg)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ccount{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:6px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ccheckout{width:100%;padding:10px 0;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--accent);color:#fff;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:5px}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ccheckout:hover{background:var(--accent-hover);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(255,107,53,.3)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ccheckout:active{transform:translateY(0)}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ccheckout:disabled{opacity:.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;box-shadow:none}}.dc-cart-floating{display:flex;position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:250;background:var(--primary,#1A237E);color:#fff;padding:9px 14px;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;box-shadow:0 -4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2);transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)}.dc-cart-floating.is-visible{transform:translateY(0)}.dc-cart-floating .cfb-label{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}.dc-cart-floating .cfb-btn{padding:7px 16px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--accent,#FF6B35);color:#fff;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s}.dc-cart-floating .cfb-btn:hover{background:var(--accent-hover,#E55A2B)}@media(min-width:1024px){.dc-cart-floating{display:none}}.dc-cart-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:300;background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);backdrop-filter:blur(3px)}.dc-cart-overlay.is-open{display:block}.dc-cart-modal{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;max-height:80vh;background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;animation:dcSlideUp .3s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)}@keyframes dcSlideUp{from{transform:translateY(100%)}to{transform:translateY(0)}}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--bg);font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-close{background:none;border:none;font-size:1.05rem;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-light);padding:3px 6px;border-radius:4px}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-close:hover{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text)}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-body{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:6px 12px;min-height:80px}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-body .dc-cart-item{padding:8px 3px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg)}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-footer{padding:10px 14px 18px;border-top:2px solid var(--bg)}.dc-cart-modal .dcm-footer .dc-ccheckout{width:100%;padding:12px 0}.hub-footer{background:#0D1642;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding:36px 20px 18px;margin-top:auto;font-size:.82rem;border-top:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}.hub-footer .inner{max-width:var(--max-w);margin:0 auto}.hub-footer .fgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:28px}@media(min-width:640px){.hub-footer .fgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}@media(min-width:960px){.hub-footer .fgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}.hub-footer .fcol h4{color:#fff;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}.hub-footer .fcol p{font-size:.76rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.52);line-height:1.7;margin:0}.hub-footer .fcol ul{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}.hub-footer .fcol ul a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:.78rem}.hub-footer .fcol ul a:hover{color:#fff;transform:translateX(4px)}.hub-footer .fcol .brand-statement{font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);line-height:1.7;margin-top:6px}.hub-footer .fcol .disclaimer-text{font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);line-height:1.7;margin:0;padding:10px 12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-radius:8px;border-left:2px solid var(--hub-accent)}.hub-footer .fbar{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);margin-top:22px;padding-top:14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;text-align:center;font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.32)}.hub-footer .fbar a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);text-decoration:underline;transition:color .2s}.hub-footer .fbar a:hover{color:#fff}@media(min-width:640px){.hub-footer .fbar{flex-direction:row;justify-content:space-between}}@media(max-width:400px){.hub-intro h1{font-size:1.25rem}.hub-logo{font-size:1.1rem}.hub-cat-btn{padding:8px 16px;font-size:.78rem}.hub-card{padding:16px}.hub-card .hc-emoji{font-size:1.8rem}}@media print{@page{margin:1.5cm .8cm}body{background:#fff;font-size:11pt;color:#000}.hub-header,.hub-cat-nav,.hub-cards,.hub-ad,.hub-divider,.hub-footer,.dc-ishop,.dc-iremove,.dc-addform,.dc-cart-sidebar,.dc-cart-floating,.dc-cart-overlay,.dc-btactions{display:none!important}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-body{box-shadow:none;padding:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-progress{display:none!important}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-panel{border:none;padding:0}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-grid{display:block}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item{padding:2px 0;background:transparent;border:none}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item:not(.is-checked){display:none!important}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked{display:flex;background:transparent}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked .dc-ibox{background:transparent;border:none;width:auto;height:auto}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked .dc-ibox svg{display:none}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-item.is-checked .dc-ibox::after{content:"☐";font-size:13pt;line-height:1}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-ichk input:checked~.dc-ibox::after{content:"☑"}#dorm-checklist-app .dc-idesc{color:#555;display:block}}.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:500;background:rgba(0,0,0,.55);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(4px);justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:20px;animation:modalFadeIn .25s var(--ease)}.modal-overlay.is-open{display:flex}.modal-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);max-width:680px;width:100%;max-height:80vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.25);animation:modalSlideIn .3s var(--ease-spring);position:relative}.modal-card .mc-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 22px 12px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--bg);flex-shrink:0}.modal-card .mc-header h2{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--text)}.modal-card .mc-close{background:none;border:none;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--text-light);cursor:pointer;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s}.modal-card .mc-close:hover{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text)}.modal-card .mc-body{overflow-y:auto;padding:16px 22px 24px;flex:1;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.75;color:var(--text)}.modal-card .mc-body h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;margin:18px 0 6px;color:var(--hub-accent)}.modal-card .mc-body h3:first-child{margin-top:0}.modal-card .mc-body p{margin:0 0 10px}.modal-card .mc-body ul{padding-left:20px;margin:6px 0 12px}.modal-card .mc-body ul li{margin-bottom:4px}.modal-card .mc-body a{color:var(--hub-accent);text-decoration:underline}.contact-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-top:6px}.contact-form label{font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-light)}.contact-form input,.contact-form textarea{padding:10px 12px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-family:var(--font);font-size:.88rem;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;background:var(--card);color:var(--text)}.contact-form input:focus,.contact-form textarea:focus{border-color:var(--hub-accent)}.contact-form textarea{min-height:100px;resize:vertical}.contact-form .cf-btn{padding:11px 0;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);background:var(--hub-accent);color:#fff;font-family:var(--font);font-size:.88rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}.contact-form .cf-btn:hover{background:var(--hub-accent-hover)}.contact-form .cf-email{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:.88rem;color:var(--text)}.contact-form .cf-email span{font-weight:700;color:var(--hub-accent)}@keyframes modalFadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}@keyframes modalSlideIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(.97)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}}</style></head><body><header class="hub-header"><div class="hub-inner"><div class="hub-logo">🛠 <span>Dorm</span>Tool</div><div class="hub-tagline">Your college transition toolkit</div><span class="hub-badge">7 Tools</span></div><div class="hub-header-sub">dormtool.com — Free interactive tools for students</div></header><main class="hub-container"><div class="hub-intro"><h1>🎒 Your <span>College Life</span>, Organized</h1><p>From move-in to move-out, from laundry to lease signing — everything you need in one place. Free, no signup, works on any device.</p><p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:.82rem"><a href="blog/what-not-to-bring-to-college/" style="color:var(--hub-accent);font-weight:600">📖 Read: 5 Things You'll Pack and Never Touch →</a></p></div><nav class="hub-cat-nav" id="hubCatNav" role="tablist"></nav><div id="hubCardsContainer"></div><div class="hub-ad">📢 AdSense Banner (728×90) – Place your ad code here</div><div class="hub-divider">⬇ Featured Tool — Scroll to use</div><section id="dorm-checklist-app"><div class="dc-header"><div class="dc-title">🎒 Dorm Essentials <span>Checklist</span></div><div class="dc-sub">Your ultimate packing & shopping list</div></div><div class="dc-body"><div class="dc-layout"><div class="dc-main"><div class="dc-progress" id="dcProgress"><div class="dc-pstats"><span id="dcChecked">0</span> of <span id="dcTotal">0</span> items</div><div class="dc-pbar"><div class="dc-pfill" id="dcPfill" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="dc-plabel" id="dcPlabel">0%</div></div><div class="dc-budget" id="dcBudget" title="Item prices shown are estimates based on typical retail prices at time of writing. Actual prices vary by brand, season, and retailer. Prices on Amazon may differ.">📊 Est. Budget: <strong id="dcBudgetTotal">~$0</strong><span class="dc-bnote">— estimated prices; actual costs vary — check Amazon</span></div><div class="dc-tabs-wrap"><div class="dc-tabs-scroll" id="dcTabs" role="tablist"></div></div><div class="dc-panel" id="dcPanel"></div><div class="dc-bottombar"><div class="dc-btsummary" id="dcSummary">Ready to pack? Start checking items off!</div><div class="dc-btactions"><button class="dc-btn-print" id="dcPrint">🖨️ Print</button><button class="dc-btn-reset" id="dcReset">🔄 Reset All</button></div></div></div><aside class="dc-cart-sidebar" id="dcCartSidebar"><div class="dc-cheader">🛒 Shopping Cart</div><div class="dc-citems" id="dcCitems"><div class="dc-cempty">Click <strong>Shop ↗</strong> on any item to add it here</div></div><div class="dc-cfooter" id="dcCfooter"><div class="dc-ccount" id="dcCcount">0 items</div><button class="dc-ccheckout" id="dcCcheckout" disabled>🛒 Shop All (0) on Amazon ↗</button></div></aside></div></div></section><div class="dc-cart-floating" id="dcCartFloat"><span class="cfb-label">🛒 <span id="dcCfloatCount">0</span> Items Selected</span><button class="cfb-btn" id="dcCfloatBtn">Checkout ↗</button></div><div class="dc-cart-overlay" id="dcCartModal"><div class="dc-cart-modal"><div class="dcm-header"><span>🛒 Shopping Cart</span><button class="dcm-close" id="dcCartModalClose">✕</button></div><div class="dcm-body" id="dcCartModalBody"></div><div class="dcm-footer"><button class="dc-ccheckout" id="dcCartModalCheckout" disabled>🛒 Shop All (0) on Amazon ↗</button></div></div></div><div class="hub-ad hub-ad--tall">📢 AdSense Banner (728×90) – Place your ad code here</div></main><footer class="hub-footer"><div class="inner"><div class="fgrid"><div class="fcol"><h4>🏠 SettleList Labs</h4><p class="brand-statement">Smart micro-utilities for campus living, moving transitions, and independent apartments. Every tool is free, private, and built for the moments that matter most in a student’s journey.</p></div><div class="fcol"><h4>🛠️ Smart Utilities</h4><ul><li><a href="dorm-checklist/index.html">📋 Dorm Checklist</a></li><li><a href="dorm-laundry-hub/index.html">🧺 Laundry Hub</a></li><li><a href="move-out-checklist/index.html">📋 Move-Out Checklist</a></li><li><a href="moving-cost-calculator/index.html">🚚 Moving Cost Calculator</a></li><li><a href="first-apartment-checklist/index.html">🏢 First Apartment Checklist</a></li><li><a href="rent-affordability/index.html">💰 Rent Affordability Calculator</a></li><li><a href="bill-splitter/index.html">💰 Roommate Bill Splitter</a></li></ul></div><div class="fcol"><h4>⚖️ Legal & Trust</h4><ul><li><a href="#" data-modal="privacy">📄 Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href="#" data-modal="terms">📜 Terms of Service</a></li><li><a href="#" data-modal="about">🧑‍💻 About Us</a></li><li><a href="#" data-modal="contact">📬 Contact Us</a></li><li><a href="mailto:hello@dormtool.com" style="font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45)">✉️ hello@dormtool.com</a></li></ul></div><div class="fcol"><h4>🔒 Earnings Disclaimer</h4><p class="disclaimer-text">SettleList Labs is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com. As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases at no extra cost to you.</p></div></div><div class="fbar"><span>© 2026 SettleList Labs. All rights reserved.</span><span>Built for students, by students.</span></div></div></footer><script>const CATEGORIES=[{id:'campus-life',label:'🎓 Campus Life',tools:['dorm-checklist','dorm-laundry-hub']},{id:'moving-transition',label:'🚚 Moving&Transition',tools:['move-out-checklist','moving-cost-calculator']},{id:'independent-living',label:'🏠 Independent Living',tools:['first-apartment-checklist','rent-affordability','bill-splitter']}];const TOOL_DATA={'dorm-checklist':{emoji:'🛏️',title:'Dorm Essentials Checklist',highlight:'Your ultimate packing&shopping list with Amazon synchronization.',url:'dorm-checklist/index.html',featured:true},'dorm-laundry-hub':{emoji:'🧺',title:'Dorm Laundry Hub',highlight:'Master laundry day!Step-by-step sorting,stain removal,and machine guides for students.',url:'dorm-laundry-hub/index.html'},'move-out-checklist':{emoji:'📋',title:'Dorm Move-Out Checklist',highlight:'Save your deposit!Get a $0-fines tracker to avoid university room penalties.',url:'move-out-checklist/index.html'},'moving-cost-calculator':{emoji:'🚚',title:'Moving Cost Calculator',highlight:'Estimate truck rentals,mileage,and supplies to budget your moving day precisely.',url:'moving-cost-calculator/index.html'},'first-apartment-checklist':{emoji:'🏢',title:'First Apartment Checklist',highlight:'High-conversion checklist tailored for outfitting your very first independent apartment.',url:'first-apartment-checklist/index.html'},'rent-affordability':{emoji:'💰',title:'Rent Affordability Calculator',highlight:'Instantly calculate your safe financial housing threshold based on net income.',url:'rent-affordability/index.html'},'bill-splitter':{emoji:'💰',title:'Roommate Bill Splitter',highlight:'Split rent,utilities,and groceries with roommates fairly without the awkward talk.',url:'bill-splitter/index.html'}};let activeCategory='campus-life';function renderHubNav(){const nav=document.getElementById('hubCatNav');nav.innerHTML='';CATEGORIES.forEach(function(cat){const btn=document.createElement('button');btn.className='hub-cat-btn'+(cat.id===activeCategory ? ' is-active' : '');btn.setAttribute('role','tab');btn.setAttribute('aria-selected',cat.id===activeCategory ? 'true' : 'false');btn.dataset.cat=cat.id;btn.innerHTML=cat.label+'<span class="cat-count">'+cat.tools.length+'</span>';btn.addEventListener('click',function(){switchCategory(cat.id);});nav.appendChild(btn);});}function renderHubCards(){const container=document.getElementById('hubCardsContainer');container.innerHTML='';CATEGORIES.forEach(function(cat){const div=document.createElement('div');div.className='hub-cards'+(cat.id===activeCategory ? ' is-visible' : '');div.id='hubCards-'+cat.id;div.style.display=cat.id===activeCategory ? 'grid' : 'none';cat.tools.forEach(function(toolId){const t=TOOL_DATA[toolId];if(!t)return;const card=document.createElement('div');card.className='hub-card';card.innerHTML='<div class="hc-emoji">'+t.emoji+'</div>'+'<div class="hc-title">'+t.title+'</div>'+'<div class="hc-highlight">'+t.highlight+'</div>'+'<div class="hc-actions">'+'<button class="hc-btn hc-btn-launch" data-tool="'+toolId+'">🚀 Launch Tool ➔</button>'+(t.featured ? '<button class="hc-btn hc-btn-preview" data-scroll-to="dc">📺 Preview</button>' : '')+'</div>';div.appendChild(card);const launchBtn=card.querySelector('.hc-btn-launch');launchBtn.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.preventDefault();if(toolId==='dorm-checklist'){document.getElementById('dorm-checklist-app').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});}else{window.open(t.url,'_blank');}});const prevBtn=card.querySelector('.hc-btn-preview');if(prevBtn){prevBtn.addEventListener('click',function(){document.getElementById('dorm-checklist-app').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});});}});container.appendChild(div);});}function switchCategory(catId){activeCategory=catId;renderHubNav();CATEGORIES.forEach(function(cat){const el=document.getElementById('hubCards-'+cat.id);if(el){el.classList.toggle('is-visible',cat.id===catId);el.style.display=cat.id===catId ? 'grid' : 'none';}});}renderHubNav();renderHubCards();const CHECKLIST_DATA=[{id:'bedding',name:'Bedding&Linens',icon:'🛏️',items:[{id:'twin-xl-sheets',name:'Twin XL Sheet Set',desc:'Standard dorm bed size — get at least 2 sets for swapping',price:29.99},{id:'mattress-topper',name:'Mattress Topper',desc:'Thin dorm mattresses are brutal;a topper saves your back',price:39.99},{id:'comforter-duvet',name:'Comforter/Duvet',desc:'Go for a lightweight all-season fill',price:49.99},{id:'pillows',name:'Pillows(2-pack)',desc:'One for sleeping,one for propping up in bed',price:24.99},{id:'mattress-protector',name:'Mattress Protector',desc:'Waterproof — bedbug-proof — a must for dorm life',price:19.99},{id:'extra-blanket',name:'Extra Blanket/Throw',desc:'Dorm AC is unpredictable;layer up',price:29.99},{id:'bed-risers',name:'Bed Risers',desc:'Gain valuable under-bed storage space',price:14.99},{id:'weighted-blanket',name:'Weighted Blanket',desc:'Helps with move-in stress and better sleep',price:39.99},]},{id:'bath',name:'Bathroom',icon:'🚿',items:[{id:'shower-caddy',name:'Shower Caddy',desc:'Carry soap,shampoo&razor to the communal shower',price:14.99},{id:'shower-flipflops',name:'Shower Flip Flops',desc:'Protect feet from communal shower floors',price:9.99},{id:'towel-set',name:'Towel Set(3-pack)',desc:'Bath,hand&washcloth — rotate for laundry day',price:24.99},{id:'bathrobe',name:'Bathrobe',desc:'Walk to shared bath without getting fully dressed',price:29.99},{id:'toiletry-bag',name:'Toiletry Bag',desc:'Keep toothbrush,deodorant&meds organized',price:19.99},{id:'overdoor-hook',name:'Over-the-Door Hook',desc:'Instant towel&robe storage without drilling',price:8.99},{id:'bath-mat',name:'Non-Slip Bath Mat',desc:'Step out of shower onto something soft&dry',price:12.99},]},{id:'desk',name:'Desk&Supplies',icon:'📚',items:[{id:'desk-lamp',name:'Desk Lamp',desc:'Dorm ceiling lights are harsh — get an LED lamp',price:24.99},{id:'power-strip',name:'Power Strip/Surge Protector',desc:'Dorms never have enough outlets — get one with USB',price:19.99},{id:'laptop-stand',name:'Laptop Stand',desc:'Raises screen to eye level;saves your neck',price:29.99},{id:'pen-holder',name:'Pen/Pencil Holder',desc:'Keep your desk clutter-free',price:9.99},{id:'sticky-notes',name:'Sticky Notes Set',desc:'For reminders,study prompts&roommate messages',price:7.99},{id:'planner',name:'Planner/Agenda',desc:'Track assignments,exams&social plans',price:14.99},{id:'bulletin-board',name:'Bulletin Board',desc:'Pin schedule,photos&important docs above desk',price:19.99},{id:'noise-headphones',name:'Noise-Canceling Headphones',desc:'Library-level focus in a noisy dorm room',price:79.99},]},{id:'electronics',name:'Electronics',icon:'📱',items:[{id:'phone-charger',name:'Phone Charger(6ft+)',desc:'Dorm outlets are far from bed — get a long cable',price:12.99},{id:'laptop-sleeve',name:'Laptop Sleeve',desc:'Protect laptop in backpack between classes',price:24.99},{id:'extension-cord',name:'Extension Cord',desc:'Reach awkwardly placed outlets',price:9.99},]},{id:'kitchen',name:'Kitchen&Food',icon:'🍳',items:[{id:'mini-fridge',name:'Mini Fridge',desc:'Keep leftovers&drinks cold(check size rules)',price:129.99},{id:'microwave',name:'Microwave',desc:'Ramen,popcorn&hot meals without leaving dorm',price:69.99},{id:'water-bottle',name:'Reusable Water Bottle',desc:'Stay hydrated — 32oz+recommended',price:19.99},]},{id:'laundry',name:'Laundry',icon:'🧺',items:[{id:'hamper',name:'Laundry Hamper/Bag',desc:'Portable — you will carry it to the laundry room',price:14.99},{id:'detergent',name:'Laundry Detergent Pods',desc:'Pre-measured pods are easier than a bottle',price:12.99},{id:'drying-rack',name:'Foldable Drying Rack',desc:'For delicates that cannot go in the dryer',price:15.99},]},{id:'storage',name:'Storage&Org',icon:'📦',items:[{id:'underbed-bins',name:'Under-Bed Storage Bins',desc:'Maximize the most underused dorm space',price:24.99},{id:'overdoor-organizer',name:'Over-the-Door Organizer',desc:'Keeps small items off the floor',price:16.99},{id:'drawer-dividers',name:'Drawer Dividers',desc:'Stop socks&accessories becoming a black hole',price:9.99},]},{id:'cleaning',name:'Cleaning',icon:'🧹',items:[{id:'wipes',name:'Disinfecting Wipes',desc:'Quick cleanups for desks,counters&door handles',price:6.99},{id:'trash-can',name:'Trash Can(small)',desc:'Under-desk size — empty it weekly',price:9.99},{id:'mini-vacuum',name:'Mini Vacuum/Dustbuster',desc:'Crumbs,dust bunnies&cereal spills',price:29.99},]},{id:'clothing',name:'Clothing',icon:'👕',items:[{id:'hangers',name:'Hangers(15-20 pack)',desc:'Velvet or slim-profile ones save closet space',price:12.99},{id:'laundry-bag',name:'Mesh Laundry Bag',desc:'Separate delicates or keep laundry contained',price:8.99},{id:'command-hooks',name:'Command Hooks(variety)',desc:'Damage-free hanging for coats,bags&towels',price:7.99},]},{id:'documents',name:'Documents&Health',icon:'📋',items:[{id:'id-folder',name:'Important Docs Folder',desc:'ID,insurance,bank info&schedule in one place',price:9.99},{id:'first-aid-kit',name:'First Aid Kit(small)',desc:'Band-aids,pain relievers,antiseptic&tweezers',price:12.99},{id:'flashlight',name:'Flashlight/Night Light',desc:'Power outages&late-night bathroom trips',price:11.99},]},];const DC_STORAGE_KEY='checklistlab_dorm';let dcState={activeTab: CHECKLIST_DATA[0].id,checked:{},customItems:{},cart:[],};let dcTotalFixed=0;CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){dcTotalFixed+=c.items.length;});function dcEnsureCustom(){CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){if(!dcState.customItems[c.id])dcState.customItems[c.id]=[];});}function dcGetCat(id){return CHECKLIST_DATA.find(function(c){return c.id===id;});}function dcGetCustom(cid){return dcState.customItems[cid]||[];}function dcGetAmazonUrl(name){return 'https://amazon.com/s?k='+encodeURIComponent(name+' dorm')+'&tag=CHECKLISTLAB-20';}function dcGetChecked(){var c=CHECKLIST_DATA.reduce(function(s,cat){return s+cat.items.filter(function(it){return dcState.checked[it.id];}).length;},0);Object.keys(dcState.customItems).forEach(function(k){(dcState.customItems[k]||[]).forEach(function(it){if(it.checked)c++;});});return c;}function dcGetCatChecked(cid){var cat=dcGetCat(cid);var c=cat ? cat.items.filter(function(it){return dcState.checked[it.id];}).length : 0;dcGetCustom(cid).forEach(function(it){if(it.checked)c++;});return c;}function dcGetCatTotal(cid){var cat=dcGetCat(cid);return(cat ? cat.items.length : 0)+dcGetCustom(cid).length;}function dcGetAllCount(){return dcTotalFixed+Object.keys(dcState.customItems).reduce(function(s,k){return s+(dcState.customItems[k]||[]).length;},0);}function dcSave(){try{localStorage.setItem(DC_STORAGE_KEY,JSON.stringify({checked: dcState.checked,customItems: dcState.customItems,cart: dcState.cart}));}catch(e){}}function dcLoad(){try{var saved=localStorage.getItem(DC_STORAGE_KEY);if(saved){var p=JSON.parse(saved);if(p.checked){CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=typeof p.checked[it.id]==='boolean' ? p.checked[it.id]: false;});});}else{CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=false;});});}if(p.customItems)dcState.customItems=p.customItems;if(p.cart)dcState.cart=p.cart;dcEnsureCustom();}else{CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=false;});});dcEnsureCustom();}}catch(e){CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=false;});});dcEnsureCustom();}}function dcRenderTabs(){var container=document.getElementById('dcTabs');container.innerHTML='';CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(cat){var btn=document.createElement('button');btn.className='dc-tab-btn'+(cat.id===dcState.activeTab ? ' is-active' : '');btn.setAttribute('role','tab');btn.setAttribute('aria-selected',cat.id===dcState.activeTab ? 'true' : 'false');btn.dataset.cat=cat.id;btn.innerHTML=cat.name+'<span class="dc-tcount">'+dcGetCatChecked(cat.id)+'/'+dcGetCatTotal(cat.id)+'</span>';btn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcSwitchTab(cat.id);});container.appendChild(btn);});}function dcRenderPanel(catId){var cat=dcGetCat(catId);if(!cat)return;var custom=dcGetCustom(catId);var cart=dcState.cart;var fixedHtml='';cat.items.forEach(function(it){var isChecked=dcState.checked[it.id];var inCart=cart.some(function(c){return c.id===it.id;});fixedHtml+='<div class="dc-item'+(isChecked?' is-checked':'')+'">'+'<div class="dc-irow">'+'<label class="dc-ichk">'+'<input type="checkbox"'+(isChecked?' checked':'')+' data-iid="'+it.id+'">'+'<span class="dc-ibox"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="2,6 5,9 10,3"/></svg></span>'+'<span class="dc-iemoji">'+(it.emoji||'')+'</span>'+'<span class="dc-iname">'+it.name+'</span>'+'</label>'+'<button class="dc-ishop'+(inCart?' is-incart':'')+'" data-iid="'+it.id+'">'+(inCart ? 'Added ✓' : 'Shop ↗')+'</button>'+'</div>'+(it.desc ? '<div class="dc-idesc">'+it.desc+'</div>' : '')+'</div>';});var customHtml='';custom.forEach(function(it){var inCart=cart.some(function(c){return c.id===it.id;});customHtml+='<div class="dc-item dc-item--custom'+(it.checked?' is-checked':'')+'">'+'<div class="dc-irow">'+'<label class="dc-ichk">'+'<input type="checkbox"'+(it.checked?' checked':'')+' data-iid="'+it.id+'">'+'<span class="dc-ibox"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="2,6 5,9 10,3"/></svg></span>'+'<span class="dc-iname">'+escHtml(it.name)+'</span>'+'</label>'+'<button class="dc-ishop'+(inCart?' is-incart':'')+'" data-iid="'+it.id+'">'+(inCart ? 'Added ✓' : 'Shop ↗')+'</button>'+'<button class="dc-iremove" data-iid="'+it.id+'" title="Remove">✕</button>'+'</div></div>';});var addFormHtml='<div class="dc-addform" data-cat="'+catId+'">'+'<input class="dc-addinput" type="text" placeholder="+Add your own item(e.g. Guitar stand)" maxlength="120">'+'<button class="dc-addbtn" type="button">Add</button></div>';document.getElementById('dcPanel').innerHTML='<div class="dc-pheader">'+'<div class="dc-ptitle">'+cat.icon+' '+cat.name+'</div>'+'<div class="dc-catactions">'+'<button class="dc-btn-selall" data-action="sel">✓ Select All</button>'+'<button class="dc-btn-desel" data-action="desel">✕ Deselect</button>'+'</div></div>'+'<div class="dc-grid">'+fixedHtml+customHtml+addFormHtml+'</div>';document.querySelectorAll('#dcPanel .dc-ichk input[type="checkbox"]').forEach(function(cb){cb.addEventListener('change',function(){dcToggleItem(this.dataset.iid);});});document.querySelectorAll('#dcPanel .dc-ishop').forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcToggleCart(this.dataset.iid);});});document.querySelectorAll('#dcPanel .dc-iremove').forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcRemoveCustom(catId,this.dataset.iid);});});var selBtn=document.querySelector('#dcPanel[data-action="sel"]');var desBtn=document.querySelector('#dcPanel[data-action="desel"]');if(selBtn)selBtn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcSelectAll(catId);});if(desBtn)desBtn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcDeselectAll(catId);});var addForm=document.querySelector('#dcPanel .dc-addform[data-cat="'+catId+'"]');if(addForm){var inp=addForm.querySelector('.dc-addinput');var aBtn=addForm.querySelector('.dc-addbtn');function doAdd(){var n=inp.value.trim();if(n.length<1)return;dcAddCustom(catId,n);inp.value='';inp.focus();}aBtn.addEventListener('click',doAdd);inp.addEventListener('keydown',function(e){if(e.key==='Enter'){e.preventDefault();doAdd();}});}}function dcToggleCart(itemId){var idx=dcState.cart.findIndex(function(c){return c.id===itemId;});if(idx>=0){dcState.cart.splice(idx,1);}else{var found=null;CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(cat){cat.items.forEach(function(it){if(it.id===itemId){found={id: it.id,name: it.name,emoji: it.emoji,amazonUrl: dcGetAmazonUrl(it.name)};}});});if(found)dcState.cart.push(found);if(!found){for(var k in dcState.customItems){var arr=dcState.customItems[k];var it=arr.find(function(i){return i.id===itemId;});if(it){found={id: it.id,name: it.name,emoji: '+',amazonUrl: dcGetAmazonUrl(it.name)};break;}}if(found)dcState.cart.push(found);}}dcSave();dcRenderCart();dcRenderPanel(dcState.activeTab);dcRenderTabs();}function dcShopAll(){var cart=dcState.cart;if(cart.length===0)return;cart.forEach(function(item){window.open(item.amazonUrl,'_blank');});}function dcRenderCart(){var cart=dcState.cart;var count=cart.length;var ciEl=document.getElementById('dcCitems');if(ciEl){if(count===0){ciEl.innerHTML='<div class="dc-cempty">Click<strong>Shop ↗</strong>on any item to add it here</div>';}else{var html='';cart.forEach(function(item){html+='<div class="dc-cart-item">'+'<span class="ci-emoji">'+(item.emoji||'•')+'</span>'+'<span class="ci-name">'+item.name+'</span>'+'<button class="ci-remove" data-iid="'+item.id+'">✕</button>'+'</div>';});ciEl.innerHTML=html;ciEl.querySelectorAll('.ci-remove').forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcToggleCart(this.dataset.iid);});});}}document.getElementById('dcCcount').textContent=count+(count===1 ? ' item' : ' items');var floatCount=document.getElementById('dcCfloatCount');if(floatCount)floatCount.textContent=count;var allDisabled=count===0;var btn1=document.getElementById('dcCcheckout');var btn2=document.getElementById('dcCartModalCheckout');if(btn1){btn1.disabled=allDisabled;btn1.textContent='🛒 Shop All('+count+')on Amazon ↗';}if(btn2){btn2.disabled=allDisabled;btn2.textContent='🛒 Shop All('+count+')on Amazon ↗';}var floatBar=document.getElementById('dcCartFloat');if(floatBar)floatBar.classList.toggle('is-visible',count>0);}function dcOpenCartModal(){var overlay=document.getElementById('dcCartModal');overlay.classList.add('is-open');var body=document.getElementById('dcCartModalBody');var cart=dcState.cart;if(cart.length===0){body.innerHTML='<div class="dc-cempty" style="padding:30px 10px;text-align:center">Your cart is empty</div>';}else{var html='';cart.forEach(function(item){html+='<div class="dc-cart-item">'+'<span class="ci-emoji">'+(item.emoji||'•')+'</span>'+'<span class="ci-name">'+item.name+'</span>'+'<button class="ci-remove" data-iid="'+item.id+'">✕</button>'+'</div>';});body.innerHTML=html;body.querySelectorAll('.ci-remove').forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){dcToggleCart(this.dataset.iid);dcOpenCartModal();});});}document.body.style.overflow='hidden';}function dcCloseCartModal(){document.getElementById('dcCartModal').classList.remove('is-open');document.body.style.overflow='';}function dcSwitchTab(catId){dcState.activeTab=catId;dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(catId);var btn=document.querySelector('#dcTabs .dc-tab-btn[data-cat="'+catId+'"]');if(btn)btn.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',inline:'center',block:'nearest'});}function dcToggleItem(itemId){if(dcState.checked.hasOwnProperty(itemId)){dcState.checked[itemId]=!dcState.checked[itemId];}else{for(var k in dcState.customItems){var arr=dcState.customItems[k];var f=arr.find(function(it){return it.id===itemId;});if(f){f.checked=!f.checked;break;}}}dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(dcState.activeTab);}function dcSelectAll(catId){var cat=dcGetCat(catId);if(cat)cat.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=true;});dcGetCustom(catId).forEach(function(it){it.checked=true;});dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(catId);}function dcDeselectAll(catId){var cat=dcGetCat(catId);if(cat)cat.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=false;});dcGetCustom(catId).forEach(function(it){it.checked=false;});dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(catId);}function dcAddCustom(catId,name){var id='cus_'+Date.now()+'_'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,6);dcState.customItems[catId].push({id:id,name:name,checked:false});dcEnsureCustom();dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(catId);}function dcRemoveCustom(catId,itemId){var found=dcGetCustom(catId).find(function(it){return it.id===itemId;});if(!confirm('Remove "'+(found ? found.name : 'this item')+'" from your list?'))return;dcState.customItems[catId]=dcState.customItems[catId].filter(function(it){return it.id!==itemId;});dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(catId);}function dcResetAll(){if(!confirm('Reset everything? This will clear your checklist AND shopping cart.'))return;CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){dcState.checked[it.id]=false;});});dcState.customItems={};dcState.cart=[];dcEnsureCustom();dcSave();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(dcState.activeTab);dcRenderCart();}function dcUpdateProgress(){var checked=dcGetChecked();var total=dcGetAllCount();var pct=total>0 ? Math.round((checked/total)*100): 0;document.getElementById('dcChecked').textContent=checked;document.getElementById('dcTotal').textContent=total;document.getElementById('dcPfill').style.width=pct+'%';document.getElementById('dcPlabel').textContent=pct+'%';var wrap=document.getElementById('dcProgress');wrap.classList.toggle('is-done',pct===100);var st=document.getElementById('dcSummary');if(pct===0)st.textContent='Ready to pack? Start checking items off!';else if(pct===100)st.textContent='🎉 All set!You are ready for move-in day!';else st.textContent="You're "+pct+"%there — keep going!";dcRenderBudget();}function dcRenderBudget(){var t=0;CHECKLIST_DATA.forEach(function(c){c.items.forEach(function(it){t+=it.price||0;});});document.getElementById('dcBudgetTotal').textContent='~$'+Math.round(t);}function dcPrint(){try{window.print();}catch(e){alert("Please use your browser’s share/menu to print.");}}function escHtml(s){var d=document.createElement('div');d.appendChild(document.createTextNode(s));return d.innerHTML;}function dcInit(){dcLoad();dcUpdateProgress();dcRenderBudget();dcRenderTabs();dcRenderPanel(dcState.activeTab);dcRenderCart();var printBtn=document.getElementById('dcPrint');printBtn.addEventListener('click',dcPrint);printBtn.addEventListener('touchstart',function(e){e.preventDefault();dcPrint();},{passive: false});document.getElementById('dcReset').addEventListener('click',dcResetAll);document.getElementById('dcCcheckout').addEventListener('click',dcShopAll);document.getElementById('dcCfloatBtn').addEventListener('click',dcOpenCartModal);document.getElementById('dcCartModalCheckout').addEventListener('click',function(){dcCloseCartModal();dcShopAll();});document.getElementById('dcCartModalClose').addEventListener('click',dcCloseCartModal);document.getElementById('dcCartModal').addEventListener('click',function(e){if(e.target===this)dcCloseCartModal();});}document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',dcInit);function openModal(id){var el=document.getElementById('modal-'+id);if(el){el.classList.add('is-open');document.body.style.overflow='hidden';}}function closeAllModals(){document.querySelectorAll('.modal-overlay').forEach(function(m){m.classList.remove('is-open');});document.body.style.overflow='';}document.querySelectorAll('[data-modal]').forEach(function(link){link.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.preventDefault();openModal(this.dataset.modal);});});document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function(){document.querySelectorAll('[data-modal-close]').forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',closeAllModals);});document.querySelectorAll('.modal-overlay').forEach(function(overlay){overlay.addEventListener('click',function(e){if(e.target===this)closeAllModals();});});});document.addEventListener('keydown',function(e){if(e.key==='Escape')closeAllModals();});</script><div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-privacy"><div class="modal-card"><div class="mc-header"><h2>📄 Privacy Policy</h2><button class="mc-close" data-modal-close>&times;</button></div><div class="mc-body"><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 17, 2026</p><p>SettleList Labs ("we," "our," or "us") operates the website <a href="https://dormtool.com" target="_blank">dormtool.com</a> and its associated tools (collectively, the "Service"). This Privacy Policy informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service.</p><h3>1. Information We Collect</h3><p><strong>Log Data.</strong> When you visit our Service, our servers may automatically record standard information sent by your browser. This may include your IP address, browser type and version, the pages you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages, and other diagnostic data.</p><p><strong>Local Storage.</strong> We use your browser's local storage to save your checklist progress, shopping cart contents, and tool preferences. This data stays on your device and is never transmitted to our servers. You can clear it at any time via your browser settings or by clicking "Reset Data" in our footer.</p><p><strong>Cookies.</strong> We use minimal cookies for core functionality. Third-party services described below may use their own cookies.</p><h3>2. Third-Party Services</h3><p><strong>Google Analytics.</strong> We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand how visitors interact with our website. GA4 may collect anonymized data about your device, browsing behavior, and geographic region. Google's privacy policy is available at <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">policies.google.com/privacy</a>. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p><p><strong>Amazon Associates.</strong> Our tool pages contain affiliate links to Amazon.com. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, Amazon may collect information about your interaction as described in <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" target="_blank">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>.</p><p><strong>Google AdSense.</strong> We may display advertisements via Google AdSense. AdSense uses cookies and web beacons to serve relevant ads based on your visits to this site and other websites. You can learn more about how Google uses your data at <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank">policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a>.</p><h3>3. Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h3><p>If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA) or California, you have the right to: <ul><li><strong>Access</strong> — Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li><li><strong>Deletion</strong> — Request that we delete your personal data (note: we do not store personal data on our servers; clearing local storage achieves this).</li><li><strong>Opt-Out</strong> — Refuse the sale of your personal information. We do not sell personal data.</li></ul> To exercise any of these rights, contact us at hello@dormtool.com.</p><h3>4. Data Security</h3><p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p><h3>5. Changes to This Policy</h3><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p><h3>6. Contact</h3><p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, reach us at: <strong>hello@dormtool.com</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-terms"><div class="modal-card"><div class="mc-header"><h2>📜 Terms of Service</h2><button class="mc-close" data-modal-close>&times;</button></div><div class="mc-body"><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 17, 2026</p><p>By accessing or using the SettleList Labs website at <a href="https://dormtool.com" target="_blank">dormtool.com</a> (the "Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p><h3>1. Use of the Service</h3><p>The tools and calculators provided on this Service are for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. They are not a substitute for professional financial, legal, or moving advice. All results generated by our calculators and checklists are estimates and should be verified independently. You use the Service at your own risk.</p><h3>2. Intellectual Property</h3><p>All content, code, design, text, graphics, and tools on this Service are the intellectual property of SettleList Labs unless otherwise noted. You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works without prior written consent. The Service is made available for personal, non-commercial use only.</p><h3>3. Affiliate Disclosure</h3><p>Our Service contains affiliate links to third-party merchants, including Amazon.com. We may earn a commission when you click these links and make a purchase. This comes at no additional cost to you. These affiliate relationships do not affect the objectivity of our tool content or recommendations.</p><h3>4. Disclaimer of Warranties</h3><p>THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, OR NON-INFRINGEMENT. WE DO NOT GUARANTEE THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, ERROR-FREE, OR FREE OF HARMFUL COMPONENTS.</p><h3>5. Limitation of Liability</h3><p>In no event shall SettleList Labs, its operators, or affiliates be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising out of or in connection with your use of the Service, even if advised of the possibility of such damages.</p><h3>6. Prohibited Uses</h3><p>You agree not to: <ul><li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws.</li><li>Attempt to scrape, crawl, or mass-harvest any content, tool data, or page structure without explicit permission.</li><li>Interfere with or disrupt the Service, servers, or networks connected to the Service.</li><li>Reverse-engineer any component of the tools or inject malicious scripts.</li></ul></p><h3>7. Changes to Terms</h3><p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p><h3>8. Governing Law</h3><p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Delaware, United States, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p><h3>9. Contact</h3><p>For questions about these Terms, reach us at: <strong>hello@dormtool.com</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-about"><div class="modal-card"><div class="mc-header"><h2>🧑‍💻 About Us</h2><button class="mc-close" data-modal-close>&times;</button></div><div class="mc-body"><p>We are a team of data-driven creators dedicated to removing the friction from college move-ins and independent living. Our personal experience — wrestling with forgotten dorm essentials, splitting utility bills with roommates, calculating rent on a student budget, and navigating the chaos of moving out — inspired us to build the tools we wish we had.</p><p>Every micro-utility on <a href="https://dormtool.com" target="_blank">dormtool.com</a> was built with a single philosophy: <strong>one problem, one page, zero fluff.</strong> No signups, no data collection, no accounts. You open the page, you get the answer, you move on with your day.</p><p>Our mission is to equip students and young adults with smart, free, private tools that turn life’s most stressful transitions into manageable checklists. Whether you are packing for your first dorm room, calculating whether you can afford that off-campus apartment, or coordinating a move-out with three roommates — we have your back.</p><p>Behind the code, we are builders who believe the web should still be lightweight, fast, and accessible to everyone. Every tool on this site is a single HTML file — no frameworks, no databases, no bloat. Just clean, vanilla JavaScript and CSS that works on any device, anywhere in the world.</p><p>Thanks for stopping by. Now go check something off your list.</p><p style="margin-top:16px;color:var(--text-light);font-size:.82rem;">— The SettleList Labs Team</p></div></div></div><div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-contact"><div class="modal-card"><div class="mc-header"><h2>📬 Contact Us</h2><button class="mc-close" data-modal-close>&times;</button></div><div class="mc-body"><p>We would love to hear from you. Whether you have a suggestion for a new tool, feedback on an existing one, or a question about our policies — drop us a message.</p><form class="contact-form" id="cfForm"><div class="cf-email" style="font-size:1rem;padding:16px 18px;background:var(--hub-accent);color:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);text-align:center"> 📧 <a href="mailto:hello@dormtool.com" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">hello@dormtool.com</a></div><p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-light);margin:6px 0 0;text-align:center">Click the email above to send us a message directly from your inbox.</p></form></div></div></div><script>if('serviceWorker' in navigator){navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js');}</script></body></html>